name: TezClicker
description:
A satire cookie clicker game where you click and delegate tez for massive gains! (Not financial advice, and no real tez were harmed in the making of this NFT) by @Rorscratch

Made in Godot 3.3.4 to celebrate HEN500K

Mint to increase tez per second and tez per click, Collect to massively increase tez per second. All jokes made in good fun
